{"tid":2446231,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"緬甸仰光2間中資廠遭火魔裝修","createTime":"2021-03-14T09:49:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-15T04:44:43.000Z","uid":184679,"like":853,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":87,"replies":[{"pid":"3e36c999fc0acc7442ca5800e85cb99548ed7aa3","tid":2446231,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T09:49:36.000Z","msg":"央視報道，緬甸最大城市仰光蘭達亞工業區有2間中資服裝廠被縱火。暫時未知是否與示威有關。<br />\n<br />\n事發當地下午2時，20多人騎電單車手拿鐵棍、斧頭和汽油衝入工廠，未有理會保安阻攔，打爛物品後，將汽油淋在廠房門口和倉庫燃點。<br />\n<br />\n工廠人員隨即撲救。 報道指，2間服裝廠分別是中資和中緬合資企業，又指仰光其他工業區一些中資服裝廠，亦面臨被縱火威脅。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://stream.881903.com/public/c74acc811e8e176890e98bf412d024ae/2021/03/7d5489eefe01ea564d584b8c7b99e58b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstream.881903.com%2Fpublic%2Fc74acc811e8e176890e98bf412d024ae%2F2021%2F03%2F7d5489eefe01ea564d584b8c7b99e58b.jpg&h=04bc83c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/international/2382941\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Finternational%2F2382941&d=wSR7%2FpLLUFbraZn9MQiPfBjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=e70f364b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/international/2382941</a>"},{"pid":"3b6f73098f1d0bf3fd443218953722469d12fb59","tid":2446231,"uid":33263,"like":248,"dislike":3,"score":245,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T09:52:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fcc6cb505781333e54afb15fc998ce3ab8fe1bb","tid":2446231,"uid":393145,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T09:53:01.000Z","msg":"雖遠必豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b0dbe8be1afdafc6f5bac57ee456eee384c21f8","tid":2446231,"uid":41343,"like":105,"dislike":11,"score":94,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T09:54:02.000Z","msg":"唔好政治化，可能係中資太賤拖糧啫"},{"pid":"2413b76ad97019b4e